<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_3835bdad-29fc-4d33-88ab-6d981b5bd57e" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>10.2.32</sptc><title id="_ea3adefe-892a-4ee6-a8fc-c7d605290706">Shower screens</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_379e2ecb-5b91-4b5a-9637-01d033b0775b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c3437f8b-16b9-42df-94cc-0cd10898fb6d">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>For a shower with a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_87f19c61-c407-4cec-b533-2f27856467a0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hob</xref>, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4663_0.4.0.xml#_013ce393-1153-476d-b268-5b06c64f9232" id="_3cb5b4dd-e9af-4a0b-b0e2-31c7eb54ccf3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower screen</xref> must be installed flush with the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1460_0.12.0.xml#_6aa99639-a955-4628-bc59-dabb3bfc8118" id="_7ff87e90-951b-49df-9c3d-08dd1152ea27" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower area</xref> side of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_fa1b9cb0-646f-471e-8451-34fb5a34d82e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hob</xref> or overhang into the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1460_0.12.0.xml#_6aa99639-a955-4628-bc59-dabb3bfc8118" id="_4eca5a70-8520-404f-8cfa-7340f6a13133" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower area</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_ab335935-5b32-428f-a753-a83bf91ab807" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a98d7ef7-c9cf-4bc3-b1f5-1691174ef42b">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>For a shower with a stepdown, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4663_0.4.0.xml#_f5fa12f7-67d1-41a7-b4e2-071dedde4e5f" id="_0da80afe-cbae-4061-b383-b074d0b26e79" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">shower screen</xref> must be installed flush with the finished vertical surface of the stepdown of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1460_0.12.0.xml#_6aa99639-a955-4628-bc59-dabb3bfc8118" id="_8a40f2c3-7848-4e26-a28b-e909ffd98422" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower area</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f5578616-52b1-456d-8a2c-87f449e0f785" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_95afe35c-82f5-4726-9031-d3e760d40dfc">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>For a shower without a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_3124d07b-c67e-43d1-9f56-fecf8edd1f2e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hob</xref> or stepdown, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4663_0.4.0.xml#_f5fa12f7-67d1-41a7-b4e2-071dedde4e5f" id="_60bffd6e-d47b-46a9-807c-d00c7f4e195c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">shower screen</xref> must incorporate or be mounted on an inverted channel, positioned over the top of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4735_0.5.0.xml#_2fb1baed-5210-4b6f-a0d1-49efc309b967" id="_9de1d22b-2fe1-432d-bf02-d466286b9c9e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">waterstop</xref>, that defines the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1460_0.12.0.xml#_6aa99639-a955-4628-bc59-dabb3bfc8118" id="_38e08ad4-d7d4-4936-8a0d-105650bdde98" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower area</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_0290273b-9030-40ff-aa9e-dd8268024098" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_06139199-b94c-4324-bc99-7761e3d4e857">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>For bath end walls and dividing walls abutting a shower, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4663_0.4.0.xml#_013ce393-1153-476d-b268-5b06c64f9232" id="_20d60f9f-f5c8-4c74-9c53-83bbd4fd847b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower screen</xref> must be positioned so that the bottom edge within the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1460_0.12.0.xml#_6aa99639-a955-4628-bc59-dabb3bfc8118" id="_8eee28d4-010f-4546-9e19-722851e64f2d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower area</xref> is either flush with the outside edge of the bath or overhanging into the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1460_0.12.0.xml#_6aa99639-a955-4628-bc59-dabb3bfc8118" id="_89ade643-3f0a-4bf8-91fa-5c1e74aae133" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shower area</xref>.</p></subclause><callout id="_0d49ed1b-4344-42b3-9543-03f57088117c"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>A self-draining sub-sill is considered to be part of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4663_0.4.0.xml#_f5fa12f7-67d1-41a7-b4e2-071dedde4e5f" id="_2aa18f6a-59d2-4fea-b780-5404608ee3a8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">shower screen</xref>.</p></callout></clause>